trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Port"></xref> instance to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection"></xref> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Legger til den angitte <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Port"> </xref> serverforekomsten til den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection"> </xref> i den angitte indeksen.

trans-unit.source: If the number of items in the collection already equals the collection's capacity, the capacity is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array before the new element is inserted.
trans-unit.target: Hvis antallet elementer i samlingen allerede er lik samlingens kapasitet, dobbel kapasiteten ved automatisk å tildele den interne matrisen på nytt før det nye objektet som settes inn.

trans-unit.source: If the value of the `index` parameter is equal to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, the specified <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Port> is added to the end of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien for den `index` parameteren er lik <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, den angitte <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Port>legges til slutten av <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.PortCollection> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Port> </xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: The elements after the insertion point move down to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: Elementene etter pekeren Flytt ned å gi plass til det nye objektet.

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, the average execution time is proportional to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden utfører en lineær søket. Gjennomsnittlig kjøringstid er derfor proporsjonalt <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>.</xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>
